data.description: Remarkable 4 Bed, 4 bath home with a loft in a guard-gated community! Opens to a gorgeous front room leading into the formal dining area w/ vaulted ceilings + decorative tiles in insets. Surround sound in family room! The amazing kitchen is complete w/ beautiful white cabinets, luxurious Caledonia Granite counters, dual islands, stunning pendant lights, double oven, walk-in pantry + upgraded stainless steel appliances! Gorgeous tile floors downstairs, wood staircase + carpet upstairs. Shutters, ceiling fans + crown moulding + eggshell finish paint throughout. All upper windows framed out for a clean/finished look! Upstairs primary bedroom has lg. balcony + 2 walk-in closets. Fully Landscaped front, back + side yards, pavers + covered patio. Spacious Garage, tankless water heater, water softener + water purifier! Community features golf, pool, sports courts, fitness center, recreation/party rooms, library, billiards, tennis, basketball, racquetball, restaurant & much more. Welcome Home!
